":153263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:52:03.000Z","msg":"深水埗mtr以外另一條最近的逃生路線：<br />\n<br />\n藍色位置係警察最脆弱的地方<br />\n藍色位置係警察最脆弱的地方<br />\n藍色位置係警察最脆弱的地方<br />\n<br />\n希望大家好好守護佢地 <br />\n<br />\n夢見藍色位置可以見到好多空的私家車 警車，高位2-4個警察有電筒， 近民居牆身有幾部cctv <br />\n另外向南係南昌站（路程10-15分鐘）， 向東係太子站， 北係白田邨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/05/232740_bf1052a6b40c3c4cec0426e615917bcf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F05%2F232740_bf1052a6b40c3c4cec0426e615917bcf.png&h=6dd9f3a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4003f6e6e29cff4444bc6b0e3a3e2ee25d06e442","tid":1416953,"uid":171509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:53:21.000Z","msg":"快啲落黎支持班義士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e56b69aa9fd9ff03a90f36496c84c4aa10d477","tid":1416953,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:53:36.000Z","msg":"和理非請你永遠記住<br />\n&quot;不割蓆&quot;唔係叫你要認同哂所有抗爭手段，你絕對可以隨時提出意見；<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">&quot;不割蓆&quot; 意思係叫你就算點都好，都唔好離隊！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n前線亦請聆聽後勸意見，深思過先選擇行動，因為你一到左前線就無人阻到你！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;絕不放棄，抗爭到底，直到勝利&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\n[ 溫故知新！] 成日話&quot;不割蓆&quot;, 都想大家深入明白咩叫&quot;不割蓆&quot;先！！(利申：不割)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1415759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1415759</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"04be7cc3a6bd9ce522bcd89b466e556df01280ed","tid":1416953,"uid":171509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:55:52.000Z","msg":"齋屌兼嘴炮就夠<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dbcac04d